author: eTN Global Editor
title: Japan Airlines launches official Instagram Account
text:
Japan Airlines launches official Instagram Account   
Aug 18, 2015 eTN   
TOKYO, Japan - Japan Airlines (JAL) launched official Instagram account to interact and engage with more customers. 
The new account will offer unique Aircraft photos, beautiful sceneries from inside the aircraft, and worldwide landscapes connected with people's everyday life to share the joy of travel and to encourage customers to travel more. 
Follow JAL on Instagram at @japanairlines_jal.
